title: Marsh hits hole-in-one at Green Meadow
content:
David Marsh aced the par-3 No. 8 Wednesday at Green Meadow Country Club. 
  
Marsh used a pitching wedge to make the 91-yard shot. It was witnessed by Tony Roberts, Jim Steffens and Ron Parsons.
